        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Water Infrastructure Trust Fund Act of 2019 </b></p> <p>The bill establishes a Water Infrastructure Trust Fund for the Environmental Protection Agency to use for capitalization grants under the clean water state revolving fund or drinking water state revolving fund. </p>]]></text>
